<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>World Clock - Home</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background-image: url('https://cdn.glitch.global/986c1b59-99fd-48b2-8bb2-9bb1e6a0c6e4/High_resolution_wallpaper_background_ID_77701419747.jpg?v=1695741872065');
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            background-position: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 10px;
            color: white;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Welcome to World Clock</h1>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Stay connected with the current time around the world.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Explore time zones and cities worldwide.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Sign up to customize your world clock.</p>
    </div>
    <a href="signup.html" class="button">Sign Up</a>
    <a href="login.html" class="button">Login</a>
